{"word":"G4949 - Συροφοίνισσα - Syrophoínissa - soo-rof-oy'-nis-sah - Syrophenician","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">Συροφοίνισσα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">Syrophoínissa</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soo-rof-oy'-nis-sah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Syrophenician</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீரோபேனிக்கேயாள் - ஸ்திரீ"},{"paragraph":"a Syrophoenician woman"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine of a compound of <a href=\"#/G4948 - Σύρος - Sýros - soo'-ros/4948\">G4948</a> and the same as <a href=\"#/G5403 - Φοινίκη - Phoiníkē - foy-nee'-kay/5403\">G5403</a>; a <i>Syro-Phaenician</i> woman, that is, a female native of Phaenicia in Syria: - Syrophenician.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}